chdb-core v26.5.0
source: https://github.com/chdb-io/chdb-core/releases/tag/v26.5.0
asset:  linux-x86_64-libchdb.tar.gz

Contains libchdb.so (the embedded ClickHouse engine), chdb.h (C API),
and chdb.hpp (C++ API). Only libchdb.so + chdb.h are used by this crate.

libchdb.so is gitignored (~530MB). Run scripts/fetch-libchdb.sh to download it.
